=Gary|accessdate=12 March 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|  [[2003\u201304 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Evan|Evan (2004)]]\n|-\n|  [[2004\u201305 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Phoebe|Phoebe (2004)]]\n|-\n|  [[2004\u201305 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Raymond|Raymond (2004)]]\n|-\n|  [[2004\u201305 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Tim|Tim (2005)]]\n|-\n|  [[2004\u201305 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Vivenne|Vivienne (2005)]]\n|-\n|  [[Cyclone Emma|Emma (2006)]]\n|-\n|  [[2006\u201307 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Pierre|Pierre (2007)]]\n|-\n|  [[2008\u201309 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Charlotte|Charlotte (2009)]] \n|-\n|  [[2008\u201309 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Ellie|Ellie (2009)]]\n|-\n|  [[2008\u201309 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Freddy|Freddy (2009)]]\n|-\n|  [[2008\u201309 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Kirrily|Kirrily]]\n|-\n|  [[2009\u201310 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Neville|Neville (2010)]]\n|-\n|  [[Cyclone Tasha|Tasha (2010)]]\n|-\n|  [[2010\u201311 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Vince|Vince (2011)]]\n|-\n|  [[2011\u201312 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Mitchell|Mitchell (2013)]]\n|-\n| [[Cyclone Oswald|Oswald]] || {{Sort|20130117|17&nbsp;\u2013 29 January 2013}} || bgcolor=#{{storm colour|A1}}|Category 1 tropical cyclone || bgcolor=#{{storm colour|A1}}|{{sort|065|65&nbsp;km/h (40&nbsp;mph)}} || bgcolor=#{{storm colour|A1}}|{{convert|991|hPa|inHg|sigfig=4|abbr=on|sortable=on}} || Eastern Australia || {{ntsp|3070000000||$}} || {{ntsp|2280000000||$}} || {{sort|6|6}} ||\n|-\n|  [[2012\u201313 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Peta|Peta (2013)]]\n|-\n|  [[Cyclone Alessia|Alessia (2013)]]\n|-\n|  [[2013\u201314 Australian region cyclone season#Tropical Cyclone Edna|Edna (2014)]]\n|-\n|  [[2013\u