-150732-5| last1 = World Health Organization| last2 = OHCHR| last3 = UN Women| last4 = UNAIDS| last5 = UNDP| last6 = UNFPA| last7 = UNICEF| title = Eliminating forced, coercive and otherwise involuntary sterilization, An interagency statement| date = 2014| url = http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/112848/1/9789241507325_eng.pdf?ua=1|author1-link= World Health Organization | author2-link = Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights }}\n* {{cite book | authorlink = Zwischengeschlecht | last = Zwischengeschlecht | date = March 2014 | chapter-url = http://intersex.shadowreport.org/public/2014-CRC-Swiss-NGO-Zwischengeschlecht-Intersex-IGM_v2.pdf | chapter = IGM \u2013 Historical Overview. Hermaphrodites in the 'Developed World': From Legal Self-Determination to IGM, Supplement 1 | title = NGO Report to the 2nd, 3rd and 4th Periodic Report of Switzerland on the Convention on the Rights of the Child (CRC)| edition = 2 | pages = 49\u201362}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commonscat-inline|Intersex}}\n{{external media | width = 210px | align = right | headerimage=  | video1 = [https://www.buzzfeed.com/lizzwarner/what-its-like-to-be-intersex \" What It's Like To Be Intersex\"], Lizz Warner, [[BuzzFeed]] }}\n\n{{Intersex}}\n{{Sex}}\n{{Sex (biology)|state=collapsed}}\n{{Reproductive health |state=collapsed}}\n{{Female congenital malformations of genital organs}}\n{{Male congenital malformations of genital organs, indeterminate sex and pseudohermaphroditism}}{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Intersex]]\n[[Category:Sex]]\n[[Category:Medical controversies]]\n", "name_user": "Naty9814", "label": "safe", "comment": "Grammatical change", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intersex"}
{"title_page": "State Forestry Corps", "text_new": "{{more footnotes|date=February 2013}}\n{{Infobox Law enforcement agency\n|agencyname  =State Forestry Corp\n|nativename  = Corpo Forestale dello Stato\n|logo = Coat of Arms of the State Forestry Corps.svg\n|abbreviation  = CFS\n|motto  = \"PRO NATURA OPUS ET VIGILANTIA\"\n|formedmonthday  = October 15\n|formedyear      = 1822\n|dissolved       = December 31, 2016\n|superseding     = ''[[Comando unit\u00e0 per la tutela forestale, ambientale e agroalimentare]]'', [[Carabinieri]]\n|country  = Italy\n|employees  = 8.500\n}}\n[[File:Corpo Forestale dello Stato.jpg|thumb|right|Officers of the State Forestry Corp.]]\nThe '''State Forestry Corps''' ([[Italian language|Italian]]: '''''Corpo forestale dello Stato''''' or '''''CFS''''') was a national [[Law enforcement in Italy|police agency in Italy]]. It was established on 15 October 1822 by [[Charles Felix of Sardinia]] as '''Amministrazione forestale per la custodia e la vigilanza dei boschi'''. [[Regions of Italy#Autonomous regions with special statute|The five Italian autonomous regions]] have their own corps of forestry police under regional or provincial control (''Corpo forestale regionale/provinciale''), which have not been disbanded.<ref>http://www.sardegnaambiente.it/corpoforestale/</ref>\nCFS was dissolved on December 31, 2016 and all personnel become militarized and absorbed  by the [[Comando unit\u00e0 per la tutela forestale, ambientale e agroalimentare]] [[Carabinieri]].\n\n==Mission==\nThe CFS had police powers and acted as a [[park ranger]] force responsible for protecting Italy's [[natural resource]]s, the environment, countryside and ecosystems, especially [[List of national parks of Italy|national parks and national forests]]. It also acted as a criminal investigative department and as a typical police force. Its specialist duties included arresting [[Poaching|poachers]], investigating [[Environmental crime|environmental violations]], [[illegal building]], [[counterfeit food]]s, safeguarding [[Endangered species|protected animal species]], enforcing [[endangered species]] laws, and preventing and fighting [[wildfire]]s through 15 regional commands and its fleet of 22 [[Aerial firefighting|fire-fighting aircraft]]. It had responsibility for managing activities related to the [[Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species]] in Italy.\n\n==Organization==\nThe CFS was an agency under the [[jurisdiction]] of the Ministry of Agriculture, Food and Forestry. It was part of the Direzione Investigativa Antimafia (DIA) (Anti-Mafia Investigation Department). The CFS was also responsible for civil protection in Italy's mountain areas and for [[disaster relief]]. If necessary, the CFS could also be used in tasks of public order in the city and any urban context.\n\n==Corporate profile==\nThe CFS's [[emergency telephone number]] for reporting forest fires was 1515. The CFS's vehicle [[livery]] was green with a white stripe and the words ''Corpo Forestale dello Stato'' in white along the side. The vehicle [[Vehicle registration plate|plates]] began with the letters \"CFS\" in red.\n\n==Rank insignia==\n{| class=\"itwiki_template_toc\" style=\"clear:both; margin-top:1em; text-align:center; float:center; border: 1px grey solid; margin: auto; width:100%\" cellpadding=\"0\"\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Senior executive positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Dirigente generale del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />dirigente generale\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Dirigente superiore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />dirigente superiore\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Primo dirigente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />primo dirigente\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Senior management positions and senior management trainees'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Vice questore aggiunto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice questore aggiunto forestale\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />commissario capo forestale\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario ruolo direttivo ordinario del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>commissario forestale (direct entry trainee) \n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario ruolo direttivo speciale del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>commissario forestale (internal recruitment trainee)\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Vice commissario del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>vice commissario (internal recruitment trainee)\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Middle management positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"24%\"|[[File:Ispettore superiore scelto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore superiore scelto<br />\n|width=\"24%\"|[[File:Ispettore superiore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore superiore\n|width=\"17%\" style=\"clear:both; border: 0px solid #999; border-left-width: 1px\"|[[File:Ispettore capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore capo\n|width=\"17%\"|[[File:Ispettore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore\n|width=\"17%\"|[[File:Vice ispettore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice ispettore\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=#228B22 border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Supervisory positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\"|[[File:Sovrintendente capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />sovrintendente capo\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" height=\"100px\"|[[File:Sovrintendente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />sovrintendente\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\"|[[File:Vice sovrintendente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice sovrintendente<br />\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Basic positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Assistente capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />{{lang|it|assistente capo}}\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Assistente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />{{lang|it|assistente}}\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Agente scelto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />agente scelto\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Agente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />agente\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Gruppo Sportivo Forestale]]\n*[[Meteomont]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.corpoforestale.it Official website] (in Italian)\n\n{{commonscat-inline|Corpo Forestale dello Stato}}\n{{Law enforcement in Italy}}\n\n[[Category:Corpo Forestale dello Stato]]\n[[Category:Forestry agencies|Italy]]\n[[Category:Defunct law enforcement agencies of Italy]]\n\n{{Italy-org-stub}}\n{{gov-stub}}\n{{forestry-agency-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{more footnotes|date=February 2013}}\n{{Infobox Law enforcement agency\n|agencyname  =State Forestry Corp\n|nativename  = Corpo Forestale dello Stato\n|logo = Coat of Arms of the State Forestry Corps.svg\n|abbreviation  = CFS\n|motto  = \"PRO NATURA OPUS ET VIGILANTIA\"\n|formedmonthday  = October 15\n|formedyear      = 1822\n|dissolved       = December 31, 2016\n|superseding     = ''[[Comando unit\u00e0 per la tutela forestale, ambientale e agroalimentare]]'', [[Carabinieri]]\n|country  = Italy\n|employees  = 8.500\n}}\n[[File:Corpo Forestale dello Stato.jpg|thumb|right|Officers of the State Forestry Corp.]]\nThe '''State Forestry Corps''' ([[Italian language|Italian]]: '''''Corpo forestale dello Stato''''' or '''''CFS''''') was a national [[Law enforcement in Italy|police agency in Italy]]. It was established on 15 October 1822 by [[Charles Felix of Sardinia]] as '''Amministrazione forestale per la custodia e la vigilanza dei boschi'''. [[Regions of Italy#Autonomous regions with special statute|The five italian autonomous regions]] have their own corps of forestry police under regional or provincial control (''Corpo forestale regionale/provinciale''), which have not been disbanded.<ref>http://www.sardegnaambiente.it/corpoforestale/</ref>\nCFS was dissolved on December 31, 2016 and all personnel become militarized and absorbed  by the [[Comando unit\u00e0 per la tutela forestale, ambientale e agroalimentare]] [[Carabinieri]].\n\n==Mission==\nThe CFS had police powers and acted as a [[park ranger]] force responsible for protecting Italy's [[natural resource]]s, the environment, countryside and ecosystems, especially [[List of national parks of Italy|national parks and national forests]]. It also acted as a criminal investigative department and as a typical police force. Its specialist duties included arresting [[Poaching|poachers]], investigating [[Environmental crime|environmental violations]], [[illegal building]], [[counterfeit food]]s, safeguarding [[Endangered species|protected animal species]], enforcing [[endangered species]] laws, and preventing and fighting [[wildfire]]s through 15 regional commands and its fleet of 22 [[Aerial firefighting|fire-fighting aircraft]]. It had responsibility for managing activities related to the [[Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species]] in Italy.\n\n==Organization==\nThe CFS was an agency under the [[jurisdiction]] of the Ministry of Agriculture, Food and Forestry. It was part of the Direzione Investigativa Antimafia (DIA) (Anti-Mafia Investigation Department). The CFS was also responsible for civil protection in Italy's mountain areas and for [[disaster relief]]. If necessary, the CFS could also be used in tasks of public order in the city and any urban context.\n\n==Corporate profile==\nThe CFS's [[emergency telephone number]] for reporting forest fires was 1515. The CFS's vehicle [[livery]] was green with a white stripe and the words ''Corpo Forestale dello Stato'' in white along the side. The vehicle [[Vehicle registration plate|plates]] began with the letters \"CFS\" in red.\n\n==Rank insignia==\n{| class=\"itwiki_template_toc\" style=\"clear:both; margin-top:1em; text-align:center; float:center; border: 1px grey solid; margin: auto; width:100%\" cellpadding=\"0\"\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Senior executive positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Dirigente generale del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />dirigente generale\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Dirigente superiore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />dirigente superiore\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Primo dirigente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />primo dirigente\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Senior management positions and senior management trainees'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Vice questore aggiunto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice questore aggiunto forestale\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />commissario capo forestale\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario ruolo direttivo ordinario del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>commissario forestale (direct entry trainee) \n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Commissario ruolo direttivo speciale del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>commissario forestale (internal recruitment trainee)\n|width=\"20%\"|[[File:Vice commissario del cfs.png|60px|]]<br>vice commissario (internal recruitment trainee)\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Middle management positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"24%\"|[[File:Ispettore superiore scelto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore superiore scelto<br />\n|width=\"24%\"|[[File:Ispettore superiore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore superiore\n|width=\"17%\" style=\"clear:both; border: 0px solid #999; border-left-width: 1px\"|[[File:Ispettore capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore capo\n|width=\"17%\"|[[File:Ispettore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />ispettore\n|width=\"17%\"|[[File:Vice ispettore del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice ispettore\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=#228B22 border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Supervisory positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\"|[[File:Sovrintendente capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />sovrintendente capo\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" height=\"100px\"|[[File:Sovrintendente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />sovrintendente\n|colspan=\"2\" width=\"33%\" align=\"center\"|[[File:Vice sovrintendente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />vice sovrintendente<br />\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=#228B22 height=\"25px\" border=0 style=\"color: white\" | '''Basic positions'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\"|\n{| width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:none;\"\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Assistente capo del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />{{lang|it|assistente capo}}\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Assistente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />{{lang|it|assistente}}\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Agente scelto del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />agente scelto\n|width=\"25%\"|[[File:Agente del cfs.png|60px|]]<br />agente\n|}\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" height=\"10px\"|\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Gruppo Sportivo Forestale]]\n*[[Meteomont]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.corpoforestale.it Official website] (in Italian)\n\n{